Package org.rd.switchboard.nexus.exporters.rda.json.graph

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JsonGraph
    Graph in JSON format Will contain 2 arrays : arrays of JsonGraph.nodes and array of JsonGraph.relationships
    JsonNode
    Node in JSON format Will contain a Node JsonNode.id, Node JsonNode.type and a map of Node JsonNode.properties Optional JsonNode.extras set can be created, containing 'root' or 'incomplete' flags
    JsonRelationship
    Relationship in JSON format Will contain JsonRelationship.from, JsonRelationship.to and JsonRelationship.type properties The from and to properties should specify an actual id of JsonNode
